title: Dan Lambton from Real Friends
itunes:title: Dan Lambton from Real Friends
description:
Dan Lambton is the vocalist from Real Friends and I had the pleasure of meeting up with him on tour a few weeks ago and we discussed expectations, sensitivity and suburb living. I think it's a really honest portrayal of what it's like to be a in a band "on the rise."
